                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9886" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0291</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1139 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华邦控股双向混改：怎么混？混得怎么样？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How to Approaching Two-Way Mixed-Ownership Reform  and Its Effectiveness: Evidence from Huabang Holdings</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">欧霞，段军山，李礼，任志宏</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广东财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华邦控股集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">32 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">民营企业；双向混改；混改动因；内部协同治理；协同治理效应；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Private enterprises; Two-way mixed-ownership reform; Motivation for mixed ownership reform; Internal collaborative governance; Collaborative governance effect;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">党的二十大报告强调，要优化民营企业发展环境，促进民营经济发展壮大。民营企业作为我国经济发展的重要力量，选择适当的混合所有制改革路径，能更好地激发民营企业创新发展的动力，为建设创新型国家和促进经济社会持续健康发展提供强有力的支撑。本案例聚焦创始人苏如春带领华邦控股成立25年来双向混改的主要经历，重点呈现华邦控股旗下华邦建投引入国有资本后如何“混”好了公司业绩、市场竞争力和品牌认可度；入股混合制企业华农保险并担任第一大股东后，如何“改”革传统国企体制，建立了一套市场化决策和运营机制，以及其中的模式和经验。通过本案例学习华邦控股双向混改的实施过程，分析混改动因、路径，对比混改前后公司治理方面的变化，掌握公司内部协同治理、协同效应等相关理论，深入理解民营企业“混”与“改”的整体逻辑。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The report of the 20th National Congress of the Communist Party of China emphasizes the need to optimize the development environment for private enterprises and promote the growth of the private economy. As an important force in China&#39;s economic development, private enterprises should choose an appropriate path of mixed ownership reform to better stimulate their innovative development and provide strong support for building an innovative country and promoting sustainable and healthy economic and social development. This case focuses on the main experience of founder Su Ruchun leading the two-way mixed ownership reform of Huabang Holdings over the past 25 years, with a focus on how Huabang Holdings has &quot;mixed&quot; its performance, market competitiveness, and brand recognition after introducing state-owned capital; After investing in a mixed ownership enterprise and becoming the largest shareholder, how to &quot;reform&quot; the traditional state-owned enterprise system, establish a market-oriented decision-making and operational mechanism, as well as the models and experiences involved. Through this case study, we will learn about the implementation process of two-way mixed ownership reform of Huabang Holdings, analyze the reasons and paths for the reform, compare the changes in corporate governance before and after the reform, grasp the relevant theories of internal collaborative governance, and gain a deeper understanding of the overall logic of &quot;mixing&quot; and &quot;reform&quot; in private enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">双向混改；混改动因；内部协同治理；协同效应；</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
